---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Faculty" description="Meet the expert teachers at Cube Classes, Meerut. Learn Physics from Daksh Narang and Chemistry from Kuldeep Chauhan.">
    <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 5%;">
        <h1 style="text-align: center; color: #042B63; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 2.5rem;">Meet Our Experts</h1>
        <p style="text-align: center; color: #666; margin-bottom: 3rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">Our founders aren't just administrators; they are passionate educators dedicated to simplifying complex concepts for board and competitive exams.</p>
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 3rem;">
            
            <div style="background: white; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
                <div style="height: 250px; background: #eee; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                    <span style="color: #999;">[Daksh Photo Placeholder]</span>
                </div>
                <div style="padding: 2rem;">
                    <h2 style="color: #0A58CA; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Daksh Narang</h2>
                    <h4 style="color: #FF6B00; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Physics Expert & Co-Founder</h4>
                    <p style="color: #444; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.6;">With a proven track record of mentoring top rankers, Daksh makes Physics intuitive. He breaks down complex mechanics and electromagnetism into logical, easy-to-grasp core principles, ensuring students don't just memorize formulas, but understand the science.</p>
                    <p><strong>Experience:</strong> 8+ Years</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="background: white; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
                <div style="height: 250px; background: #eee; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                    <span style="color: #999;">[Kuldeep Photo Placeholder]</span>
                </div>
                <div style="padding: 2rem;">
                    <h2 style="color: #0A58CA; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Kuldeep Chauhan</h2>
                    <h4 style="color: #FF6B00; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Chemistry Expert & Co-Founder</h4>
                    <p style="color: #444; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.6;">Kuldeep transforms Chemistry from a subject of rote memorization into a logical framework. Specializing in Organic and Physical Chemistry, his structured teaching methodology has consistently helped students maximize their scoring potential in NEET and JEE.</p>
                    <p><strong>Experience:</strong> 8+ Years</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>